{"tid":598771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我在此正式宣告 所有KPOP韓流文化都係垃圾","createTime":"2018-03-19T21:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T23:54:29.000Z","uid":98915,"like":36,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5612edad84da4047e67c984fc7b1ec29f90a33","tid":598771,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T21:56:51.000Z","msg":"女嘅整容 閪女人 只係靠賣弄性感 與一樓一嘅雞無異<br />\n<br />\n男嘅生得似女人 胸無半點墨水 靠年輕消費白痴女性市場 與牛郎無異<br />\n<br />\n影視產業正頭唔知講咩好 原本韓電影都有期有好嘢 例如原罪犯個啲 但近代就算鳩數啦 得一兩套有討論價值<br />\n<br />\n音樂個方面 我諗識音樂嘅巴打都明 根本零鑑賞性 特別係啲編曲垃撚圾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身為歌星居然可以冇唱功 只係班靠跳舞嘅垃圾咁同跳鋼管舞嘅雞/鴨有咩分別？ 咁樣叫音樂？ 好在佢哋mixing班後期佬叫幾勁先救返少少冇咁柒<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面我直頭唔想講 將個部隊鍋收返落你老母個閪到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n化妝個方面 其實還可以 但根本唔適合大部份人 依家好多人無論好醜都撻到成個嘴紅撚哂 屌你老母百鬼夜行咁款<br />\n<br />\n我縱觀成個世界唔同流行文化歷史 我敢講一句未有一個流行文化係內涵係差得過韓流<br />\n<br />\n利申：非任何文化打手 只針韓流垃圾文化"},{"pid":"28206b278f1219547f64a13968306726992fdda3","tid":598771,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T22:11:23.000Z","msg":"55<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d550618da3db8f2fac46fac069aa7cb51c6e0dd5","tid":598771,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T22:47:45.000Z","msg":"收到 唔該"},{"pid":"12c07adc79c6e0f7e936eb2510470cae276a2730","tid":598771,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T23:16:55.000Z","msg":"yes sir"},{"pid":"6cf7d041e04fd2ccb85a84bc12446929cc8072ef","tid":598771,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T23:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/072033_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F072033_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=35dc677d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f9f316be499341cbcd89a5ab381c89c630e983e","tid":598771,"uid":17348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T23:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/072650_01451cd0ed46d916a1e2ef2ff44b925e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F072650_01451cd0ed46d916a1e2ef2ff44b925e.png&h=cab7825a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c61175b90024987f936d3b4f6b33e5a707ef930","tid":598771,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T23:31:37.000Z","msg":"環保post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db108d72a42ba506583aca187fb11196656a7e0","tid":598771,"uid":35815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T23:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66698d238683b4e968933c94541fd35051beca9b","tid":598771,"uid":128014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5db108d72a42ba506583aca187fb11196656a7e0","tid":598771,"uid":35815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T23:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"食軍糧以為自己食上等菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43242c7e3aa8364a5dc7d73902cb03d47784b8a0","tid":598771,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530f2809dec5bf276c6df5690074da31d9172e1d","tid":598771,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T23:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}